# Intentfile - declared future intent for lcb-website
# Roadmap towards verified container deployment via stapeln pipeline

version: 1

future:
  stapeln-integration:
    - "Build lcb-wordpress image via Containerfile with Chainguard wolfi-base."
    - "Sign with cerro-torre (Ed25519 + Dilithium5-AES hybrid)."
    - "Deploy via selur-compose.yml with svalinn gateway + vordr runtime."
    - "Replace Verpex shared hosting with self-hosted verified container stack."

  security-evolution:
    - "Migrate policy hashes from SHA-256 to SHAKE3-512 (FIPS 202)."
    - "Implement Ed448 + Dilithium5 hybrid signatures for CTP manifests."
    - "Add Kyber-1024 (ML-KEM-1024) post-quantum key exchange for bundle transfer."
    - "Enable SPHINCS+ fallback for all hybrid PQ signature systems."
    - "Formal verification of crypto primitives via Coq/Isabelle."

  consent-hardening:
    - "Full AIBDP enforcement at svalinn gateway level (HTTP 430)."
    - "Cedar policy engine integration for fine-grained consent rules."
    - "Consent audit trail in feedback-o-tron with in-toto attestations."

  accessibility:
    - "WCAG 2.3 AAA certification for Sinople theme."
    - "ARIA landmark audit with axe-core in CI."
    - "Semantic XML validation in build pipeline."

  members-platform:
    - "Self-service NUJ membership verification via API integration."
    - "Encrypted member communications channel."
    - "Privacy-preserving member directory (opt-in only)."

  monitoring:
    - "UptimeRobot integration for availability monitoring."
    - "Wordfence alerting pipeline into feedback-o-tron."
    - "LiteSpeed Cache hit-rate dashboards."
    - "Security header compliance monitoring (securityheaders.com API)."

  content-pipeline:
    - "WP-CLI automated content deployment from content/ markdown files."
    - "GitOps-style content updates: merge to main triggers WP-CLI sync."
    - "Markdown-to-WordPress block converter for content/pages/."
